$interpreted: Puggi: Hey, slow down a bit!

Pang: Blame yourself for having short legs.
Can't you fly?

Puggi: Hmph, if I were to be serious about flying, 
I'll be so good at it I'll even scare myself!
Pang: Then get serious about flying.
Puggi: But I don't want to scare myself!

Puggi: Hmm? Did you just smile?
I think this is the first time I've seen you smile.
Pang: No, you've made a mistake.
Puggi: Nah, I'm pretty sure that I saw the edge of your mouth curl slightly upwards.
Pang: ... Keep yapping and I'll send you flying for real!
Stewart: Hmph, seems that you guys are enjoying your lives quite well!
Pang: You guys again?

Stewart: I told you that I will definitely return to take that damn bird back.
Boys, prepare yourselves!
Pang: Crap, used too much strength.
Stewart: Get 'em!
Pang: Now it's your turn! Show me what you got!
Stewart: H, HELP~~
Pang: HEY! FAT BIRD! Are you alright?
Puggi: ... Uhh... Where's everyone else? Pang?

Puggi: ... Eh, did he die in the fight...
It took me a long time to find a minion to protect me too...

Pang: ... Minion?
So you are just using me all this time?
Puggi: Pang! So you are still alive!

Pang: I was just squashed underneath it...
Didn't think that it would allow me to hear your true intentions.
Puggi: No, that's not what I mean. In fact, I...
Pang: You're afraid that they will come back for you, that's why you approached me, all because you want me to do your dirty work?
Puggi: I, I really didn't mean to do that...
Pang: Yao's actions got me exiled from the Alliance, and the Tigers also lost all power and prestige within the East Alliance.
Pang: Now, even you are just taking advantage of me, aren't you?
Pang: If you want a bodyguard, go find someone else to exploit. Bet there's plenty out there.
Puggi: Pang, let me explain...
Pang: Get lost!!!
